('788a0949-9aa1-5841-a0e4-5189c6fe6de9', 1, 'a_tier_deep_dive_completed', 'positive', NULL, 'Deep-dive outcome: passed_a. Items checked: 1_owner_age: Seth Malone Gibson est age ~78 (RPLS #2000 granted 1978, + 30 age + 18 = ~78). License-tenure proxy. OV65 not verified.; 2_successor_verification: PASSED — candgsurveyors.com homepage live-fetch (2026-05-16): only Seth Gibson RPLS #2000 listed as staff; no second RPLS, no family-surname successor, no associate or partner. TBPELS RPLS join confir; 3_comptroller_status: Firm operating per active website + Yelp current as of June 2025 + multi-listing.; 4_disciplinary: No disciplinary action surfaced.; 5_civil_filings: None surfaced.; 6_building_ownership: Operations address 1210 N Thompson St, Conroe TX 77301 (Montgomery County) — likely owner-occupied freestanding office (typical of long-tenured surveyors). CAD verification would confirm.; 7_value_add_thesis: (See sharpened thesis.) Strong fit for acquire-self in a high-growth metro.; 8_metro_pull: Conroe Montgomery County = MAJOR GROWTH METRO (north Houston suburbs). Top 5 fastest-growing TX counties. Significant development volume = boundary + topo + construction stake-out demand at peak. Laye', 'phase_5_a_tier_deep_dive', NULL, '2026-05-16'),
('ea9e3c58-588d-5a9e-8928-08b9a4d215a3', 1, 'owner_age_proxy_rpls_tenure', 'positive', NULL, 'Senior RPLS Richard V. Hall (TBPELS license #2001) granted 1978-08-24 → 48yr tenure. TX RPLS requires 4yr college + 4yr supervised survey-in-training + state exam (typically earned at age 28-35); est. owner age ~78.', 'tbpels_rpls_roster', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rpls_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
