('ea9e3c58-588d-5a9e-8928-08b9a4d215a3', 4, 'low_pe_attention_vertical', 'positive', NULL, 'TX land surveying = LOW-PE-ATTENTION vertical. Only Bowman Consulting (NASDAQ:BWMN) + Westwood Professional Services (Endeavour Capital) are PE-backed rollup platforms active in TX surveying. Large-AEC strategics (Stantec/WSP/AECOM/Kimley-Horn/Cobb Fendley/LJA) only bolt-on $5M+ rev firms. Sub-$5M independent universe (Houston, Harris County) structurally under-targeted = opportunity zone. ETA/search-fund appetite emerging fast 2024-2026 per Stanford Search Fund Study (top-15 ETA vertical).', 'verticals.md skill config + Stanford Search Fund Study + Bowman 10-K filings', 'https://pels.texas.gov/roster/ls_rosters.html', '2026-05-16'),
